  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You've developed your internal toxic glands, allowing you to further manipulate your caustic cells. You gain the following benefits;</p><p>Increase your Constitution or Intelligence score by 1, to a max of 20.</p><p>Your Caustic Cell total increase by half your Constitution modifier (min 1).</p><p>You regain a number of expended Caustic Cells equal to your full proficiency bonus when you finish a short rest.</p><p>As a bonus action, you may expend any number of Caustic Cells to regain 2d6 hit points per cell.</p>",
